    ABOUT

    Who We Are

    Sonic Whales Marketing has been forged from a sheer passion for cryptocurrency and the Blockchain industry, keeping a keen eye on what makes every project different and what makes them tick. Distinguishing the winners from the losers. What makes a project successful?


    Our founders pondered long and hard over this question and came to the conclusion that most early projects fail due to three key reasons; marketing, community and professionalism.


    At Sonic Whales Marketing, we have highlighted these three key reasons and have perfected a strategic approach to make a successful project, utilising it in over 10 projects in 2021 alone. We help to create safe, exciting and most of all, profitable launches for all parties involved.
